
### OFF-001: Create termination review
POST http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": "{{employeeId}}",
  "initiator": "MANAGER",
  "reason": "PERFORMANCE",
  "terminationDate": "2025-02-15T00:00:00Z",
  "contractId": "{{contractId}}",
  "performanceDataId": "perf_12345",
  "hrComments": "Multiple warnings on file, final review completed"
}

###
### Create termination for termination due to warnings
POST http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": "{{employeeId}}",
  "initiator": "HR",
  "reason": "MISCONDUCT",
  "terminationDate": "2025-02-10T00:00:00Z",
  "contractId": "{{contractId}}",
  "hrComments": "Serious misconduct incident documented"
}

###
### Get termination by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination/{{terminationId}}

###
### Get all terminations
GET http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination

###
### Get terminations by status (UNDER_REVIEW)
GET http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination?status=UNDER_REVIEW

###
### Get terminations by employee
GET http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination?employeeId={{employeeId}}

###
### Update termination status
PATCH http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination/{{terminationId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "hrComments": "Approved by HR Director on 2025-01-15"
}

###
### Get termination approval payload
GET http://localhost:8000/offboarding/termination/{{terminationId}}/approval-payload

